---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Base
  title="About Us"
  description="We're wellness enthusiasts and K-Beauty nerds writing about what we actually do, eat, and use."
>
  <Header />

  <main class="flex-1">
    <article class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8 py-16">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <span class="inline-block text-[11px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-sage-400 mb-5">About</span>
        <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl sm:text-5xl text-charcoal tracking-tight leading-[1.1] mb-8">
          Real people, real routines,<br class="hidden sm:block" /> real results.
        </h1>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-3xl prose mt-8">
        <p>
          We started Rooted Glow because we were tired of wellness content that felt either too clinical or too woo-woo. We wanted something in between. practical, grounded, and actually tested by real people.
        </p>

        <h2>What We Believe</h2>
        <p>
          Health isn't a product you buy. It's built from how you eat, move, sleep, and care for yourself. daily, consistently, without overthinking it. We lean toward ancestral nutrition (real food, minimal processing), functional movement, and skincare routines inspired by Korean beauty traditions.
        </p>

        <h2>Our Editorial Standards</h2>
        <p>
          Everything we publish is based on personal experience, peer-reviewed research, or both. We don't accept sponsored posts. When we recommend a product, it's because we've used it ourselves. usually for weeks before writing a word about it.
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>No paid placements or sponsored content</li>
          <li>All health claims are backed by cited sources</li>
          <li>Product recommendations come from personal testing</li>
          <li>We update articles when new evidence emerges</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>The Team</h2>
        <p>
          We're a small group of writers and editors who share a common obsession: figuring out what actually works. in the kitchen, at the gym, and in front of the bathroom mirror. Some of us came from fitness backgrounds, others from the K-Beauty rabbit hole, and a few from both.
        </p>

        <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
        <p>
          Have a question, a correction, or a story to share? We'd love to hear from you. Drop us a line at <strong>hello@rooted-glow.com</strong>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </article>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Base>
